type: software
title: "AgentKG: Conversational Memory as a Knowledge Graph"
abstract: >
  AgentKG stores and retrieves conversational AI agent memory as a live,
  queryable knowledge graph. It provides persistent, structured memory for
  AI agents with semantic search, topic clustering, entity tracking, and
  MCP integration — enabling agents to recall prior context, build knowledge
  over time, and reason over their interaction history.
